findings.title: Out of gas
findings.description: The functions includeInReward() and _getCurrentSupply() use loops that can cause an OUT_OF_GAS exception if the excluded addresses list is too long.

findings.title: Owner privileges (In the period when the owner is not renounced)
findings.description: The contract owner has excessive privileges, including changing tax and liquidity fee, maximum transaction amount, excluding from fees and max transaction amount, locking and unlocking. The owner can even retake privileges after ownership renouncement.
